column5: Hi all, got out again for an hour, actually had 3 hours to spare but it eats into fishing time taking Berty the drone out. Bite was half an hour later than last time, probably because of the clear bright conditions. Got some nice walleye and some bigger ones this time, a 25” and 22” with three just under 18” and a pike, not a bad hours fishing if you ask me.
Now that's a great outing. Love those sunset pics with the fish, well done.  Cheers

When I 1st tried to open the video it said "Hmm...Can't seem to reach this page". I pushed the quote feature and the video appeared then. Then when I tried to open it my lap top shut down. The bottom right of the screen said "F1 reboot" or something similar. Strange.
amazing report once again!  Love the videos.  Thanks for taking the time to post it Cheers!
